Sport Champion of Third Round 
  
Sport Club do Recife was Champion of Pernambuco 1982. 

Top Scorers:

Baiano (Náutico) 40; Joãozinho (Sport) e Heider (Náutico) 19; Roberto (Sport) 15; Édson (Sport) e Nélson Borges (Náutico) 14.

